description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the root rendering context and includes necessary imports for React, ReactDOM, stylesheet, and App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to enable rendering of React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the created root node.
